				"string" : "This screenshot contains an elaborate scene with three panes. In the first pane, we have a Coder on the {{gtClass:GtLudoGame}} class, in which we have expanded the {{gtMethod:GtLudoGame>>moveTokenNamed:}} method, and in that method we expanded a message. Then we looked for references by pressing a shortcut; this produced a second pane with a filter tool. In that filter tool we scrolled down to {{gtMethod:GtLudoRecordingGameExamples>>#gameShowingAllMoves2}}, a method that happens to be an example (which is like a test that returns an object). We expanded the method and executed the example by clicking the button in the contextual toolbar of the method coder. This produced the third pane containing an inspector with the result. As a small detail: when the mouse hovered over the button, a tooltip appeared."
